      • testSpaceTable

        public void testSpaceTable()
                    throws java.lang.Exception
        We use the SpaceTable VTI as our primary test VTI to verify that that VTI table mappings in general are working as expected. So this method does a lot more than the other VTI test methods; the other test methods just do sanity checks to make sure that the mapping from "SYSCS_DIAG." to the actual VTI class names in question is working correctly.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
